                                                                  HIBERNATE-VALIDATOR
                                                                  
                                                                  
                                                                  
                     validating the data from the client with certain conditions                                             
                     
                     
                     
                     @NotBlank  == NotBlank && NotNull
                     @NotNull
                     @Size    - used for String, Collection, Map
                     @Length  - used specifically for String 
                     @Email
                     @Positive
                     @Negative
                     @PositiveOrZero
                     @NegativeOrZero
                     @Future
                     @FutureOrPresent
                     @Past
                     @PastOrPresent
